We have them, genuine VW. I think this one will fit your application:

http://www.germansupply.com/xcart/customer/product.php?productid=16605

You have to be ingenious to attach them, as the factory ones are swaged on.
I have used a tiny machine screw drill & tapped into the block on the
backing plate.


